name: Why do women kill
description:
Have you ever heard the story of a certain Katherine Knight? We’ll come back to that later
And today I want to talk to you about women-killers, because it’s not customary to talk about it. Why do women kill? Psychological disorders? A desire for revenge? A grievance for a bad childhood? Every option is possible. But one thing is certain. Every female murderer plans and prepares her own murder. So the mysterious beauty plotted her murderous murder.
